commentable_entity.ask: Reopening the Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp Abuse Case for actual Justice to be carried out.
commentable_entity.title: Johnny Depp: Reopening the Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp Abuse Case for actual Justice to be carried out.
commentable_entity.description:
As we all know what has gone on for the last 4 years. The horrendous injustice carried out against Johnny Depp via Amber Heard and her Laywers. I have made this petition to hopefully get over 5 million signatures and I pray alot of donations on another site because the donations will go towards, or pay in full for not 1 but 2 of the world's leading behavioural specialists to look at every tiny aspect from the start to the end and to report there findings to Johnny Depp's Laywer. I myself am starting an English Literature degree and my aim is also to become a Solicitor to defend people who need it the most. I can only feel so sorry for a great actor that this has happened to. If it had happened to me, god knows that I would not have coped with it all.

To whoever that reads this and can feel it, know it, like myself that Johnny Depp is innocent and had this awful thing happen then please sign it.

All documentation of each signature (IP address) I will ask Change to document so no bloating will be going on and therfore no accusations can be made of "a individual signing over 500+ times" as Warner Bros has accused other petitions of this and Amber Heard.

I see that JD has 8.9 million followers on his Instagram, so, I am asking all of you, please sign and donate and finaly get this terrible thing put right.

I can be found on Twitter and will be posting then kinks all over it for the fundraising aspect.

comment:
I think they both hit each other and each should take responsibility for how they hurt each other but I think Johnny Depp still deserves to have his career back. 
It’s not fair that she still has hers but he can’t play roles at all. He should be allowed to have his roles back if they both struck or hurt each other and she has her career but he doesn’t have his. I don’t think it’s fair either way to take one persons career away or the other’s while one person keeps theirs if they both hit each other and did the same things. Either make both of their careers suffer for that or just let Johnny have his career back. Im more for the latter of just allowing him have his career back.
